ecided: \"Knight's Cross yes, 28 April 1945\". Tenschert was a member of the AKCR.<ref>Scherzer 2007, p. 178.</ref>|group=\"Note\"}}\n| [[German Army (Wehrmacht)|Heer]] || <span style=\"display:none\">15-H</span>''[[Major (Germany)|Major]]'' || Commander of the II./Festungs-Regiment Mohr ([[Siege of Breslau|fortress Breslau]])<ref name=\"Fellgiebel p420\">Fellgiebel 2000, p. 420.</ref> || {{dts|format=dmy|1945|April|28}} || {{center|\u2014}} || {{center|\u2014}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{sortname|Heinrich|Terharen}}\n| [[German Army (Wehrmacht)|Heer]] || <span style=\"display:none\">12-H</span>''[[Leutnant]]'' of the [[Military reserve force|Reserves]]<ref name=\"Scherzer p739\"/> || Leader of the 5./Grenadier-Regiment 956<ref name=\"Scherzer p739\"/><ref name=\"Fellgiebel p420\"/> || {{dts|format=dmy|1944|December|9}}<ref name=\"Scherzer p739\"/> || {{center|\u2014}} || {{center|\u2014}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{sortname|Heinrich|Teriete}}\n| [[German Army (Wehrmacht)|Heer]] || <span style=\"display:none\">12-H</span>''[[Leutnant]]''<ref name=\"Scherzer p739\"/> || ''[[Zugf\u00fchrer (military)|Zugf\u00fchrer]]'' (platoon leader) in the schwere Panzer-J\u00e4ger-Abteilung 653<ref name=\"Scherzer p739\"/><ref name=\"Fellgiebel pp420,506\">Fellgiebel 2000, pp. 420, 506.</ref> || {{dts|format=dmy|1943|July|22}}<ref name=\"Scherzer p739\"/> || {{center|\u2014}} || {{center|\u2014}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{sortname|Hermann|Tesch}}\n| [[German Army (Wehrmacht)|Heer]] || <span style=\"display:none\">12-H</span>''[[Leutnant]]'' of the [[Military reserve force|Reserves]]<ref name=\"Scherzer p739\"/> || Leader of the 11./Grenadier-Regiment 67<ref name=\"Scherzer p739\"/><ref name=\"Fellgiebel p420\"/> || {{dts|format=dmy|1944|June|9}}<ref name=\"Scherzer p739\"/> || {{center|\u2014}} || {{center|\u2014}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{sortname|Karl-Heinz|Tesch}}\n| [[German Army (Wehrmacht)|Heer]] || <span style=\"display:none\">05-H</span>''Stabsgefreiter''<ref name=\"Scherzer p7