-1218-500, Gerhard Thyben.jpg|100px]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{sortname|Hans|Thylmann}}\n| [[German Army (Wehrmacht)|Heer]] || <span style=\"display:none\">15-H</span>''[[Major (Germany)|Major]]''<ref name=\"Scherzer p745\"/> || Commander of the I./Panzergrenadier-Regiment 26<ref name=\"Fellgiebel p423\"/><ref name=\"Scherzer p745\"/> || {{dts|format=dmy|1945|February|18}}<ref name=\"Scherzer p745\"/> || {{center|\u2014}} || {{center|\u2014}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{sortname|Ernst|Tiburzy}}\n| [[Volkssturm]] || <span style=\"display:none\">15-H</span>''[[Volkssturmmann]]'' (holding a rank equivalent to ''[[Major (Germany)|Major]]'')<ref name=\"Scherzer p745\"/> || Battalion leader in the Volkssturm-Bataillon 25/82 in the fortress [[K\u00f6nigsberg]]<ref name=\"Fellgiebel pp423,506\">Fellgiebel 2000, pp. 423, 506.</ref>{{refn|According to Scherzer as battalion leader in the Volkssturm-Bataillon 25/82 in the [[Kampfgruppe]] Mikosch (fortress [[K\u00f6nigsberg]]).<ref name=\"Scherzer p745\"/>|group=\"Note\"}} || {{dts|format=dmy|1945|February|10}}<ref name=\"Scherzer p745\"/> || {{center|\u2014}} || {{center|\u2014}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{sortname|Ekkehard|Tichy}}\n| [[Luftwaffe]] || <span style=\"display:none\">13-L</span>''[[Oberleutnant]]''<ref name=\"Scherzer p745\"/> || ''[[Staffelkapit\u00e4n]]'' of the 9.(Sturm)/[[Jagdgeschwader 3]] \"Udet\"<ref name=\"Fellgiebel pp423,506\"/>{{refn|According to Scherzer as pilot in the IV./[[Jagdgeschwader 3]] \"Udet\".<ref name=\"Scherzer p745\"/>|group=\"Note\"}} || style=\"background:#e3d9ff;\" align=\"left\" | {{dts|format=dmy|1945|January|14}}*<ref name=\"Scherzer p745\"/> || [[Killed in action]] 16&nbsp;August&nbsp;1944<ref name=\"Fellgiebel p423\"/> || {{center|\u2014}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{sortname|Werner|Tiedtke}}\n| [[German Army (Wehrmacht)|Heer]] || <span style=\"display:none\">12-H</span>''[[Leutnant]]''{{refn|According to Scherzer as ''[[Leutnant]]'' of the [[Military reserve force|Reserves]].<ref name=\"S