st time in September 1944, in January 1945 and April 1945. The Federal Archive holds neither record of nomination, rejection nor a file card of any proceedings. The order commission of the [[Association of Knight's Cross Recipients]] (AKCR) never processed his case either.<ref name=\"Scherzer p180\">Scherzer 2007, p. 180.</ref>|group=\"Note\"}}\n| [[German Army (Wehrmacht)|Heer]] || <span style=\"display:none\">12-H</span>''[[Leutnant]]'' || Chief of the 1./Sturmgesch\u00fctz-Brigade 300 (F)<ref name=\"Fellgiebel p424\"/> || {{dts|format=dmy|1945|May|7}} || {{center|\u2014}} || {{center|\u2014}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{sortname|Adolf-Hilmar von|Tippelskirch}}\n| [[German Army (Wehrmacht)|Heer]] || <span style=\"display:none\">13-H</span>''[[Oberleutnant]]''<ref name=\"Scherzer p746\"/> || Chief of the 1./Artillerie-Regiment 3 (motorized)<ref name=\"Scherzer p746\"/><ref name=\"Fellgiebel p424\"/> || {{dts|format=dmy|1941|September|29}}<ref name=\"Scherzer p746\"/> || {{center|\u2014}} || {{center|\u2014}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#C0EFBA\" align=\"left\" | {{sortname|Kurt von|Tippelskirch}}+\n| [[German Army (Wehrmacht)|Heer]] || <span style=\"display:none\">19-H</span>''[[Generalleutnant]]''<ref name=\"Scherzer p746\"/> || Commander of the [[30th Infantry Division (Wehrmacht)|30. Infanterie-Division]]<ref name=\"Scherzer p746\"/><ref name=\"Fellgiebel p424\"/> || {{dts|format=dmy|1941|November|23}}<ref name=\"Scherzer p746\"/> || Awarded 539th Oak Leaves 30&nbsp;July&nbsp;1944<ref name=\"Scherzer p746\"/> || {{center|\u2014}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{sortname|Herbert|Tischendorf}}\n| [[German Army (Wehrmacht)|Heer]] || <span style=\"display:none\">14-H</span>''[[Hauptmann]]''<ref name=\"Scherzer p746\"/> || Company chief in [[509th Heavy Tank Battalion (Germany)|schwere Panzer-Abteilung 509]]<ref name=\"Scherzer p746\"/><ref name=\"Fellgiebel pp424,506\">Fellgiebel 2000, pp. 424, 506.</ref> || {{dts|format=dmy|1945|March|11}}<ref name=\"Scherzer p74