ard|T\u00f6dt||Toedt, Heinz-Eduard}}\n| [[German Army (Wehrmacht)|Heer]] || <span style=\"display:none\">13-H</span>''[[Oberleutnant]]'' of the [[Military reserve force|Reserves]]<ref name=\"Scherzer p747\"/> || Chief of the 1./Artillerie-Regiment 66<ref name=\"Fellgiebel p424\"/><ref name=\"Scherzer p747\"/> || {{dts|format=dmy|1944|September|2}}<ref name=\"Scherzer p747\"/> || {{center|\u2014}} || {{center|\u2014}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" style=\"background:#C0EFBA\" align=\"left\" | {{sortname|Werner|T\u00f6niges||Toeniges, Werner}}+\n| [[Kriegsmarine]] || <span style=\"display:none\">13-M</span>''[[Oberleutnant zur See]]''<ref name=\"Scherzer p747\"/> || Commander of [[Schnellboot]] ''S-102'' in the 1. Schnellbootflottille<ref name=\"Fellgiebel p424\"/>{{refn|According to Scherzer as commander of [[Schnellboot]] ''S-102''.<ref name=\"Scherzer p747\"/>|group=\"Note\"}} || {{dts|format=dmy|1941|February|25}}<ref name=\"Scherzer p747\"/> || Awarded 143rd Oak Leaves 13&nbsp;November&nbsp;1942<ref name=\"Scherzer p747\"/> || {{center|\u2014}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{sortname|Hermann|T\u00f6nnjes||Toennjes, Hermann}}{{refn|According to Scherzer name is spelled [[Hermann T\u00f6nnies]] and as [[Aide-de-camp]] in the Stab of the I./Grenadier-Regiment 255.<ref name=\"Scherzer p747\"/>|group=\"Note\"|name=\"T\u00f6nnjes\"}}\n| [[German Army (Wehrmacht)|Heer]] || <span style=\"display:none\">10-H</span>''[[Oberf\u00e4hnrich]]''<ref name=\"Scherzer p747\"/> || [[Aide-de-camp]] in the I./Grenadier-Regiment 255<ref name=\"Fellgiebel p424\"/><ref group=\"Note\" name=\"T\u00f6nnjes\"/> || {{dts|format=dmy|1944|April|20}}<ref name=\"Scherzer p747\"/> || {{center|\u2014}} || {{center|\u2014}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | {{sortname|Hans|T\u00f6pfer||Toepfer, Hans}}\n| [[Luftwaffe]] || <span style=\"display:none\">13-L</span>''[[Oberleutnant]]''<ref name=\"Scherzer p747\"/> || ''[[Staffelkapit\u00e4n]]'' of the 1./[[Schlachtgeschwader 3]]<ref name=\"Fellgiebel pp424,506\"/>{{refn|Accordin